---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Cash Homebuyers America">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 text-gray-900 mt-1 mb-20 space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
        <p>
            Cash Homebuyers America (operated by DJW Company, LLC) is committed
            to protecting the privacy and security of your personal information.
            This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your
            information, as well as your rights. By using our website and
            services, you agree to this policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Property address</li>
            <li>
                Other information voluntarily submitted through our website
                forms
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            We may also collect technical information such as your IP address,
            browser type, device information, and website usage data to help
            improve our website and services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Your information may be used to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Respond to your inquiries</li>
            <li>Evaluate your property</li>
            <li>Facilitate potential real estate transactions</li>
            <li>
                Contact you by phone call, text message, or email regarding your
                property inquiry
            </li>
            <li>Schedule appointments</li>
            <li>Provide property-related updates</li>
            <li>Improve our website and services</li>
            <li>Maintain business records</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Phone and Text Communications</h2>
        <p>
            By submitting your contact information, you consent to receive
            communications regarding your property inquiry by phone call, text
            message, and email, including appointment reminders, confirmations,
            property updates, and general communications.
        </p>
        <p>Message frequency varies.</p>
        <p>Message and data rates may apply for text messages.</p>
        <p>
            You may opt out of text messages at any time by replying <b>STOP</b> or
            request additional information by replying <b>HELP</b>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>
            We do not sell, share, or transfer your personal information to
            third parties for their marketing purposes.
        </p>
        <p>We may share your information only when reasonably necessary to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Operate our business</li>
            <li>Work with trusted service providers</li>
            <li>Facilitate a real estate transaction</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
            <li>Protect our rights or property</li>
            <li>Complete a merger, acquisition, or business transfer</li>
            <li>Carry out any purpose for which you have provided consent</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Data Security</h2>
        <p>
            We implement reasonable safeguards designed to protect your
            information from unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure.
            However, no method of electronic transmission or storage is
            completely secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
        <p>
            We may use cookies and similar technologies to improve website
            performance, understand visitor behavior, personalize your
            experience, and measure advertising effectiveness.
        </p>
        <p>
            We may also use analytics and advertising platforms to help us
            understand website usage and improve our marketing efforts.
        </p>
        <p>You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Your Privacy Rights</h2>
        <p>
            You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your
            personal information by contacting us.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you are a California resident, you may also exercise any
            applicable rights available under California law by contacting us
            using the information below.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
            Our website and services are intended for adults. We do not
            knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years
            of age.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect
            changes in our practices or for legal, operational, or regulatory
            reasons. Any updates will be posted on this page.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
            If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please
            contact us:
        </p>
        <p>
            Email: <a
                href="mailto:dan@cashhomebuyersamerica.com"
                class="text-[#1E73BE] hover:underline"
                >dan@cashhomebuyersamerica.com</a
            ><br />
            Phone: <a
                href="tel:+14804704065"
                class="text-[#1E73BE] hover:underline">(480) 470-4065</a
            >
        </p>
    </div>
</Layout>
